{"tid":1436620,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(重開）關於獨立調查委員會及雙普選實質框架","createTime":"2019-08-09T10:21:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T17:59:45.000Z","uid":280136,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f11912eb1f0fe5d36c8af7d5bdc61b23d1766400","tid":1436620,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:21:09.000Z","msg":"經歷左兩個月嘅風波，我地不斷重申五大訴求<br />\n當中實行雙普選及獨立調查委員會為之重要<br />\n一個係真正還政於民，一個係徹查黑警濫權<br />\n但咁耐以黎好似冇一個solidified嘅框架去制定兩者嘅實質操作<br />\n<br />\n最後可能會好似831咁監生比件垃圾你食<br />\n到時候政府回應左民意，但你班廢青唔接受<br />\n豈不是真&middot;民意逆轉？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有見及此，小弟愚昧咁思考左幾樣基本框架，希望可以brainstorm一下各位大大<br />\n<br />\n首先關於雙普選<br />\n<br />\n普選的對象包括：行政長官及立法會<br />\n首先講下行政長官先<br />\n參考目前選舉委員會嘅框架，首先你要係1200人嘅選委入面取得1/8(150)人嘅票就可以進入下一輪成為候選人<br />\n<br />\n而候選人需要取得過半數(600票)就可以當選行政長官<br />\n<br />\n係廢除選舉委員會，實現真普選時，考慮嘅應有：<br />\n1.參選人需要取得一定數目（1萬？5萬？10萬？）嘅合資格選民提名，交去一個獨立評議會(由市民選出每一屆評議會)以評議該參選人是否合資格+有冇犯罪紀錄+健康狀況+是否值得信任等<br />\n2.一旦評議會信任參選人合資格，參選人將成為候選人，進入普選階段<br />\n<br />\n又或者唔要評議會？(因為同831框架太似）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而立法會則必須：<br />\n1.徹底廢除功能組別，所有議席由地區直選產生<br />\n2.議員不得持有外國國籍，以保障「愛國愛港」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3.政黨不得在選舉舉行前一星期作任何政治宣傳or接觸市民<br />\n<br />\n而普選立法會可以融合埋區議會嘅概念成為「兩院制」，參考美國嘅眾議院同參議院咁<br />\n參議院：18區每一區選5個議員<br />\n眾議院：根據18區每一區嘅人數劃分<br />\n<br />\n至於獨立調查委員會，小弟構思左一個咁嘅框架<br />\n<br />\n主席1人 終審法院法官/首席法官<br />\n<br />\n副主席1人 終審法院法官/高等法院法官<br />\n<br />\n委員：<br />\n<br />\n醫學界代表 (負責檢視警方是否濫用武力造成嚴重或永久性傷殘)<br />\n<br />\n法律界代表(負責檢視警方是否在違反法律的情況下「執法」)<br />\n<br />\n警察代表(負責檢視警方是否違反警察通例)<br />\n<br />\n紀律部隊代表(負責檢視警方是否違反紀律部隊的操守)<br />\n<br />\n公務員代表(負責檢視警方是否違反公務員的操守)<br />\n<br />\n市民代表(負責檢視警方是否對市民造成滋擾、威嚇甚至作出傷害的行為)<br />\n<br />\n暫時都係思索到咁多下，歡迎大家入黎討論"},{"pid":"780e701eec8c06af3814e3f7144885e2fac46248","tid":1436620,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:22:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ed384c24fa3ddec59d64b0a4348cee95319108ff","tid":1436620,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:23:24.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"17f401d83152079fcaf81449df25c1d26d5e4a56","tid":1436620,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:23:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"82e9c8e6af1ed1e6b4f55ca8d2e53bda758cbff2","tid":1436620,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:24:08.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7d80a74756cc0f7e4e08e429d2bf7619dfe1415b","tid":1436620,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:25:12.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"c29d011f1da868669a7cb069acae213036fbf344","tid":1436620,"uid":63639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:26:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"dc38d6a7354beb0f9495dffe05a5d5d61f3b08f7","tid":1436620,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:26:56.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0d4d55d22dae8e491cba6dbe7fff7b03598697be","tid":1436620,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:27:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"53f796e981881ef7692e76797d96ebe864037f74","tid":1436620,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:27:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ad37eb68b2a2e7c51416a43d1c57c6055bdd2b84","tid":1436620,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:27:41.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bfed61cadc09ec1e79fc577ea055895336c884df","tid":1436620,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:27:58.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"703e11043e36650fab5cff856a373f951d9ef2e8","tid":1436620,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:28:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6df4b165a59d0bb47156d6ff7d5d4476db62cec6","tid":1436620,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:28:17.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5e350f0bfc73dc01d92f3b9c2fba27c7a2975b47","tid":1436620,"uid":93962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:28:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"49ea8170a0240e83d5f3cef2a6d43a9c16300cc6","tid":1436620,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:29:24.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"217d8d7eeb4f1d0974f144174be991fe1ba9f0da","tid":1436620,"uid":94502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:29:28.000Z","msg":"區議會法定權力起碼要返到以前市政局水平"},{"pid":"b2604a0c4a975325880f1e4d44613002256b795d","tid":1436620,"uid":33984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:29:31.000Z","msg":"piah"},{"pid":"5a6ba41f2a3ff3adb57fa0d363ecc9c0136757b6","tid":1436620,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:29:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"30191a6dfb6f217ffac44f1dead3fdd2abfdb902","tid":1436620,"uid":134801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:29:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3f7c8c9b9e235e4d4109cd281d94a2dd86fa857","tid":1436620,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:30:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3abffdcae3c4b84c7e2a4cc8d376fe6e8746c15a","tid":1436620,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:30:35.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"68c0b1d308ac52f55ccc84d73a3f7d88dd9ce737","tid":1436620,"uid":280136,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"217d8d7eeb4f1d0974f144174be991fe1ba9f0da","tid":1436620,"uid":94502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:29:28.000Z","msg":"區議會法定權力起碼要返到以前市政局水平"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:33:37.000Z","msg":"講起上黎，正正係因為老懵董殺左市政局同搞問責制，搞到行政長官權力無限大<br />\n應該比返政務司權力，做真正公務員之首"},{"pid":"d83ccfc7ae101d94152d2ded7bd5def5dd07a1cb","tid":1436620,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:33:47.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"84fc2bad40d820904ce6e1533a3f29afda2de34a","tid":1436620,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:34:36.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"392e4f7d6b41bd12b8786fcb17b68d5781386bb4","tid":1436620,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:35:24.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"de845e2331197c1af445c1224ffa87b92c10dad9","tid":1436620,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:35:36.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"eeaa3821a3ca83299dd0602ba1dc09baca196672","tid":1436620,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:36:48.000Z","msg":"我覺得獨立委員會個scope都好緊要<br />\n好多人，例如林鄭今日，講到獨立調查委員會淨係查警察，但個範圍其實可以包好多野，包括成場運動點發生點解發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成個政府d指令點黎<br />\n<br />\nThe Chief Executive in Council may appoint one or more Commissioners (hereinafter referred to as a Commission) to inquire into the conduct or management of any public body, the conduct of any public officer or into any matter whatsoever which is, in his opinion, of public importance"},{"pid":"32e73c9d52605f06f965abe241f52f9817684d3a","tid":1436620,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:37:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d30bc4d4f5d2a6db2e93c8f65c2a12150aedf26f","tid":1436620,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:38:35.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"faf0d322c16e6f1ae245de0ee5c5b173cd4f4fb4","tid":1436620,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:38:51.000Z","msg":"push"}